l数据库.html","link":"","permalink":"http://someone120.tk/Go%E6%93%8D%E4%BD%9CMysql%E6%95%B0%E6%8D%AE%E5%BA%93.html","excerpt":"","text":"Go操作Mysql数据库 Go没有内置的驱动支持任何数据库，但是Go定义了database/sql接口，用户可以基于驱动接口开发相应数据库的驱动。但缺点是，直接用 github.com/go-sql-driver/mysql 访问数据库都是直接写 sql，取出结果然后自己拼成对象，使用上面不是很方便，可读性也不好。 下载包 go get github.com/go-sql-driver/mysql 使用 123456789101112131415161718192021222324252627package mainimport ( \"database/sql\" \"fmt\" _ \"github.com/go-sql-driver/mysql\" \"time\")//数据库连接信息const ( USERNAME = \"root\" PASSWORD = \"123456\" NETWORK = \"tcp\" SERVER = \"127.0.0.1\" PORT = 3306 DATABASE = \"test\")func main()&#123; conn := fmt.Sprintf(\"%s:%s@%s(%s:%d)/%s\",USERNAME, PASSWORD, NETWORK, SERVER, PORT, DATABASE) DB, err := sql.Open(\"mysql\", conn) if err != nil &#123; fmt.Println(\"connection to mysql failed:\", err) return &#125;&#125;","categories":[],"tags":[{"name":"coding","slug":"coding","permalink":"http://someone120.tk/tags/coding/"}]},{"title":"我吃了个番茄","slug":"我吃了个番茄","date":"2020-04-10T04:01:15.000Z","updated":"2020-04-10T04:18:46.872Z","comments":true,"path":"我吃了个番茄.html","link":"","permalink":"http://someone120.tk/%E6%88%91%E5%90%83%E4%BA%86%E4%B8%AA%E7%95%AA%E8%8C%84.html","excerpt":"","text":"它竟然是柿子味的！","categories":[],"tags":[]},{"title":"quarkmc","slug":"quarkmc","date":"2020-03-19T15:08:41.000Z","updated":"2020-03-19T15:17:07.112Z","comments":true,"path":"quarkmc.html","link":"","permalink":"http://someone120.tk/quarkmc.html","excerpt":"","text":"Quarkmc 是一个用于 Minecraft Bedrock Edit 的 ws 服务器。他的存在让 Minecraft Bedrock Edit 大大增加了扩展性。 安装 1.克隆或者下载 zip 包。 2.移动到目录 3.执行 npm install 插件 插件是 Quarkmc 的灵魂。如果没有了插件，就像人类失去了智力。 安装插件 1.下载插件并放在 Quarkmc 的目录中。 2.执行 node plugin.js install 插件的名称。 编写插件 这一部分等会再说 w","categories":[],"tags":[]}],"categories":[],"tags":[{"name":"coding","slug":"coding","permalink":"http://someone120.tk/tags/coding/"}]}